.SH "NAME"
sfconvert \- convert audio files
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fBsfconvert\fR \fIinfile\fR \fIoutfile\fR [\fIoutput options\fR]
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
The sfconvert command converts an audio file to another file format or data format\&.
